  - `npm install robodogcli`  
  - `npm install robodog`  
- **Python**:  
  - `pip install robodogcli`  
  - `pip show -f robodogcli`  
  - `python -m robodogcli.cli --help`  
  - `pip install --upgrade requests tiktoken PyYAML openai playwright pydantic langchain` (optional)  

