## Build & Run  

```bash
# Clone or unzip robodog
cd robodog
python build.py
open ./dist/robodog.html
```

```bash
npm install robodoglib  
npm install robodogcli  
npm install robodog  
pip install robodogcli  
pip show -f robodogcli  
python -m robodogcli.cli --help  
python -m playwright install
```

